{"tid":468794,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵個女朋友係咪真係咁難","createTime":"2017-11-14T16:55:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T21:53:23.000Z","uid":134484,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a9d53ceba18a1cae98fb6aec6af25ceeb1967cfd","tid":468794,"uid":134484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T16:55:05.000Z","msg":"中學時期讀男校再加性格內向所以識唔多人<br />\n識得嗰啲女仔唔係貪錢,收兵就係鐘意偽韓<br />\n(識個女仔因為有人送iphone即刻做咗人哋條女)<br />\n我最憎比人利用同唔理韓風所以都冇乜人啱傾<br />\n班兄弟話我遇人不淑  叫我入u慢慢搵<br />\n然後入到u識到啲女仔好多又係性格唔啱冇興趣...<br />\n難得搵到啲啱傾嘅   點知又有男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n18歲都就嚟  一次拖都未拍過<br />\n見到人哋入到嚟一兩個禮拜就出pool<br />\n拍住拖上堂 食飯 去圖書館 住hall 真係好羨慕<br />\n見到佢哋就覺得自己好撚失敗<br />\n而家感覺好似做乜都冇動力咁<br />\n連啲兄弟都叫我搵條女照亮我人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟搵到個啱嘅人又要係單身係咪真係咁難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f6c46ed288e8f3e63efb7be6ecb386e98ff17f2","tid":468794,"uid":35248,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T20:48:36.000Z","msg":"見到18歲已經唔使討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8caff6cc6a18c155d4d9df1a3bbc32adbf6c2eec","tid":468794,"uid":147002,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T21:24:28.000Z","msg":"靜啦，我大過你a0都未出叫春post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6284359629683f8773b063ceb7756fbb1406e63","tid":468794,"uid":132898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T21:53:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到18歲已經唔使討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n此post已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}